{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/st1.png?t=1737689790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An ancient Lovecraftian evil has returned to earth unleashing a deadly flesh organism upon humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One by one the the governments and the infrastructures of humans fell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the Aftermath of these events, you are part of what's left of the army and it is up to you to ensure the survival of the human species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/st2.png?t=1737689790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/ezgif-3-cef928edd6.gif?t=1737689790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During combat, you take control of your strike team ensuring they will fulfill their objectives and return safely by choosing the optimal equipment and best tactical approach.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">real-time strategy controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;turn-based&quot; possibility with active pause command mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/st3.png?t=1737689790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/city_management_trans.gif?t=1737689790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 <br>As a commander, you will take control of a military convoy where you can: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">decide the equipment of your strike team </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">assign personnel to different survival tasks </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">craft better equipment </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">research new technologies </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">choose the path you want the convoy to take </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">manage resource priority </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">train your personnel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/st5.png?t=1737689790\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chapter 1 - introduction to the game lore and new game options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chapter 2 - The journey begins, assemble your convoy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chapter 3 - Open-World</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chapter 4 - Multiple endings + 2 different totally unique paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, the game folder also contains a Map Editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Good luck Commander! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Enemy kills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2529770/fe644bba4e7d8311d786f5